{"id":60,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">&nbsp;徐庆全，上个世纪八十年代完成学士（山东曲阜师范大学历史系）和硕士（首都师范大学历史系）的学业。硕士师从著名史学家宁可教授，以研究吐鲁番出土文书为专业。毕业后留校作吐鲁番出土文书专职研究</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年。因在改革生机勃勃的八十年代成长，对现实政治、经济非常关注，读书兴趣在“厚今薄古”，转而自习中共党史。后从事编辑工作，先在《炎黄春秋》，后作为《百年潮》的创办人之一于调入中共中央党史研究室。现任《炎黄春秋》杂志副总编辑。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">&nbsp;在近</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的编辑过程中，一直坚持编辑学者化的观点，专注于当代思想意识形态和当代文学和的研究。著有《知情者眼中的周扬》（经济日报出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2003</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）、《文坛拨乱反正实录》（浙江人民出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）；《周扬与冯雪峰》（湖北人民出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2005</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）；《风雨送春归——新时期文坛思想解放运动记事》（河南大学出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2005</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）；《革命吞噬他的儿女——丁玲陈企霞反党集团案纪实》（香港中文大学出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）；《名家书札与文坛风云》（中国文史出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）。编有《周扬新时期文稿》（山西人民出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年）；《中国经验——改革开放</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年高层决策回忆》（山东人民出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2008</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）；《亲历</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年》（中国文史出版社，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2008</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">）。</SPAN></FONT></P>","title":"徐庆全","time":1205519113000}